@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8080
@adminUsername = admin
@ownerUsername = li_ming
@employeeUsername = chen_xu
@password = 123456
@repeatableAdminNodeProjectName = create_node_admin_case_{{$timestamp}}
@repeatableOwnerNodeProjectName = create_node_owner_case_{{$timestamp}}
@repeatablePersonalNodeProjectName = create_node_personal_case_{{$timestamp}}
@completedProjectId = 1
@missingProjectId = 999999
@invalidProjectId = 0

### 提示：正常路径会先创建临时项目，再创建阶段节点，因此可以重复回放。
### 提示：当前使用固定 completedProjectId=1（官网重构）验证“项目已完成不允许新增节点”。
### 当前为 12.2 创建阶段节点 的 RED 用例；接口未实现前，相关请求会先失败，后续据此补实现。

### 正常路径：管理员登录
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{adminUsername}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 正常路径：管理员创建临时项目
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "{{repeatableAdminNodeProjectName}}",
  "description": "用于验证管理员创建阶段节点接口。",
  "planned_start_date": "2026-04-01",
  "planned_end_date": "2026-04-30"
}

> {% client.global.set("repeatableAdminCreateNodeProjectId", response.body.data.id); %}

### 正常路径：管理员在临时项目末尾追加阶段节点
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableAdminCreateNodeProjectId}}/nodes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "需求梳理",
  "description": "用于验证管理员默认追加创建阶段节点。",
  "planned_start_date": "2026-04-05",
  "planned_end_date": "2026-04-10"
}

### 正常路径：管理员继续创建第二个阶段节点，默认仍追加到末尾
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableAdminCreateNodeProjectId}}/nodes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "原型设计",
  "description": "用于验证连续创建时仍默认追加到末尾。",
  "planned_start_date": "2026-04-11",
  "planned_end_date": "2026-04-14"
}

### 正常路径：管理员登出
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 异常路径：未登录创建阶段节点，预期 401
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableAdminCreateNodeProjectId}}/nodes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "未登录节点",
  "planned_start_date": "2026-04-11",
  "planned_end_date": "2026-04-12"
}

### 正常路径：项目负责人登录
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{ownerUsername}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 正常路径：项目负责人创建临时项目
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "{{repeatableOwnerNodeProjectName}}",
  "description": "用于验证项目负责人创建阶段节点接口。",
  "planned_start_date": "2026-04-01",
  "planned_end_date": "2026-04-30"
}

> {% client.global.set("repeatableOwnerCreateNodeProjectId", response.body.data.id); %}

### 正常路径：项目负责人为自己的临时项目创建阶段节点
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableOwnerCreateNodeProjectId}}/nodes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "开发实现",
  "description": "用于验证项目负责人创建阶段节点。",
  "planned_start_date": "2026-04-06",
  "planned_end_date": "2026-04-15"
}

### 正常路径：项目负责人登出
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 正常路径：普通员工登录
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{employeeUsername}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 异常路径：普通员工为非本人负责项目创建阶段节点，预期 403
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableAdminCreateNodeProjectId}}/nodes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "越权节点",
  "planned_start_date": "2026-04-11",
  "planned_end_date": "2026-04-12"
}

### 正常路径：普通员工创建个人自用临时项目
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "{{repeatablePersonalNodeProjectName}}",
  "description": "用于验证普通员工个人自用项目的阶段节点权限。",
  "planned_start_date": "2026-04-01",
  "planned_end_date": "2026-04-30"
}

> {% client.global.set("repeatablePersonalCreateNodeProjectId", response.body.data.id); %}

### 正常路径：普通员工登出
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 异常路径：重新登录管理员
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{adminUsername}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 异常路径：管理员为普通员工个人自用项目创建阶段节点，预期 403
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatablePersonalCreateNodeProjectId}}/nodes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "管理员越权节点",
  "planned_start_date": "2026-04-11",
  "planned_end_date": "2026-04-12"
}

### 异常路径：project_id 小于等于 0，预期 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{invalidProjectId}}/nodes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "非法项目ID",
  "planned_start_date": "2026-04-11",
  "planned_end_date": "2026-04-12"
}

### 异常路径：请求体不是 JSON 对象，预期 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableAdminCreateNodeProjectId}}/nodes
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "name": "invalid_body_case"
  }
]

### 异常路径：缺少 name，预期 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableAdminCreateNodeProjectId}}/nodes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "planned_start_date": "2026-04-11",
  "planned_end_date": "2026-04-12"
}

